The original skill encodes the methodology from Dr. Kristin Sainani's
"Writing in the Sciences" course at Stanford University. The video lectures
are available at https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLVc-QdfGfSl2Ntc6CvIP83Nj_uHTSdNSw
under a CC-BY license.

The v2.0 extensions incorporate writing principles from:
- Kip S. Thorne, "Some Specific Tips About Technical Writing" (Caltech, 1987)
- John A. Wheeler, "Wheeler's Rules of Writing," assembled by Edwin F. Taylor,
  Am. J. Phys. 67(11), November 1999
